        "subject": "=⚠️ High Price Alert — {{ $json.product_name }}",
        "html": "=<h2 style=\"color:#c0392b\">⚠️ High Price Alert Detected</h2>\n<p>The automated procurement system has detected a supplier quote exceeding the market benchmark by more than 15%.</p>\n\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"10\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;font-family:Arial;font-size:14px\">\n  <tr style=\"background:#2c3e50;color:white\">\n    <td><b>Field</b></td>\n    <td><b>Value</b></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td><b>Product</b></td>\n    <td>{{ $json.product_name }}</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr style=\"background:#f9f9f9\">\n    <td><b>Material</b></td>\n    <td>{{ $json.material }}</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td><b>Standard</b></td>\n    <td>{{ $json.standard }}</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr style=\"background:#f9f9f9\">\n    <td><b>Market Benchmark</b></td>\n    <td>${{ $json.benchmark_price }}</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td><b>Best Supplier</b></td>\n    <td>{{ $json.best_supplier }}</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr style=\"background:#f9f9f9\">\n    <td><b>Best Price</b></td>\n    <td>${{ $json.best_price }}</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr style=\"background:#fdecea\">\n    <td><b>⚠️ Flagged Supplier</b></td>\n    <td>Gulf Marine Supplies, Dubai</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr style=\"background:#fdecea\">\n    <td><b>⚠️ Flagged Price</b></td>\n    <td>$850 — 28.4% above benchmark</td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n\n<br>\n<p style=\"color:#7f8c8d;font-size:12px\">\n  This is an automated alert from the Maritime Procurement AI System.<br>\n  Please review and take appropriate sourcing action.\n</p>",
        "options": {}
